description:
Jellyfish.tech is a Ukraine-based IT company who has been helping the partners create superb tech products from scratch and upgrade the existing ones.
Our team has proven expertise in building:
PPM tools;
Network analysis applications;
Corporate and personal messengers, chats & chatbots;
SEO tools;
RESTful APIs.
We create stable web product to satisfy any customer needs, starting from startups to big companies. 
Technological stack we focus on:
Python/ Django for backend;
JavaScript/ Angular/ React for frontend;
MySQL and PostgreSQL for database.
The developers from Jellyfish.tech are curious and flexible, thus, going beyond the above-mentioned technologies is not a problem for us.
Being a small agency, we choose quality over quantity, that's why only the professionals, who stay passionate about what they're doing work for Jellyfish.tech, making the transparency, expertise, and integrity the crucial parts of our corporate culture.
